// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-0468 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 4eb56684-6bc1-514b-8081-8d2dbc1856b4

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:5*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:6*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.04*")
